They want faster and easier deportations.

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:31.260
That is what they want.

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:34.420
And, um, I will mention now the points.

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:37.300
So people that commit crimes

00:00:38.280 --> 00:00:42.620
should be now deported more easy than before.

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:48.500
So any crimes, avoid them.

00:00:49.280 --> 00:00:51.620
Before people will get document,

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:53.420
they can commit crime

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:55.880
and nothing big will happen to them

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.340
apart from the punishment.

