But now they say

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:00.680
if you commit even small,

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:01.860
small crimes

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:05.100
multiplied once in one year,

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.520
they can depart you then.

