00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:29.460
and you're supposed to be departed,

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:30.980
they will pick you

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:33.640
very short before the deportation date.

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:36.420
So they can bring you direct to the airport.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:38.280
Another thing is,

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:41.080
if you had a lawyer in the asylum case,

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:41.600
you will not

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.520
not get the chance to get a lawyer

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:45.300
if you're in deportation prison.

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:49.540
But if no lawyer was involved in your asylum case,

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:52.280
then you have the chance to get

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:53.920
inside the deportation prison

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:56.320
a lawyer then.

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.480
Another point is

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:00.100
that the police now is allowed

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:05.220
to search in different Rooms in your Adderall house

00:02:05.240 --> 00:02:08.780
