00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:10.840
like documents,

00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.100
letters, papers,

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.940
phones and all that.

00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:18.360
Before they was only allowed to search your own room,

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:21.040
