00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:22.420
in the whole house.

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:26.280
Then they are also permitted to pick you in the night

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.900
before the deportation.

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:29.560
Anytime in the night.

00:02:29.560 --> 00:02:32.240
